column2: SELECT m.ID, m.RAdeg AS ra1, m.DEdeg AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning, s.class, s.subclass, s.ra AS ra2, s.dec AS dec2 into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.nepwise AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.RAdeg, m.DEdeg, #) AS n LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON n.objid = s.specObjID
